room_title: Escape room "National Heist: Locking Down Liberty" by 5th Street Escape Room in Pittsburgh
room_description: Your team of thieves is making an attempt at sealing the Declaration of Independence. This could be the greatest heist of the century, but you only have a small window of opportunity to pull it off! The trick is, the declaration is sealed behind a 9,000lb vault door. Do you have what it takes?
